  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About the Game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Banana-Shape is a clicker Game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win random banana shapes and grow your collection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clicks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every hour we give you a random item</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple rarity items to grow your collection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your items to change your skin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn higher rarity items by using higher rarity skins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consume your items to obtain different ones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ranking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Future Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many more uses for your items</p></li></ul>",
